item.title: CVE-2023-36925|2023-07-11T04:05:45.179Z -- sap_se -- sap%20solution%20manager%20%28diagnostics%20agent%29
item.description: SAP Solution Manager (Diagnostics agent) - version 7.20, allows an unauthenticated attacker to blindly execute HTTP requests. On successful exploitation, the attacker can cause a limited impact on confidentiality and availability of the application and other applications the Diagnostics Agent can reach.
